Subject: Let's Connect About Your Application!

Body:
<html><body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#222222;font-size:14px;">
<p><strong>Hi [applicant_first_name],</strong></p>

<p>Thank you so much for applying for the [job_title] role at Outsourced Pro Global! We're excited to learn more about you and share what makes our team a great place to grow.</p>

<p>We'd love to invite you for a quick 15-20 minute Zoom chat with our Recruitment Specialist. This is a great chance for us to get to know each other better and see if this role and our company are the right fit for you.</p>

<p><strong>Interview details:</strong><br>
Date: [Date]<br>
Time: [Time] [Timezone]<br>
Zoom Link: [Link]</p>

<p><strong>Friendly Reminders:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>Kindly connect 10 minutes early to make sure your camera and microphone are working properly.</li>
<li>Use your laptop or PC for this interview.</li>
<li>Make sure that your Full Name and the role you are interviewing for are reflected in the Zoom meeting.</li>
<li>Please be reminded that this is a formal meeting, so be in business attire.</li>
<li>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to any of our recruiters at +61 489 275 966 (AU) or through their mobile number.</li>
</ul>

<p>Yours in Outsourced Pro Global,</p>

[signature]
</body></html>
